name: orchidite transfusion (growth/phase)
description:
2480 . 3508 350 dpi dream scroll

Update, #478088 , 7299 mhz, -878 -88 -45 -10.

Upon igniting acquamarine ashes of this pearl-like
substance, I can see it decay. It's half-life marks
at unsual spots, and by the passing of days, blooms
a new life mechanism of synthesis. The blooming is
accompanied by a sharp growth of pale, colorless
thorns. Almost unpenetrable, it bursts a projection
of molecular hologram, forming a flux of randomized
compositions that keep progressing and reducing it
to nothing. On trying to understand, i've developed 
a new sense of color, as the combinations dazzle and
abuse the capacity of light processing of my ocular mod.
